{"tid":744770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星飲咗支過期水(國泰)","createTime":"2018-07-16T07:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T10:30:02.000Z","uid":80069,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7a667ad888e9c5fc707c92c3727eddd39231e252","tid":744770,"uid":80069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"報時:05:12<br />\n航班:CX178<br />\n當享用完美味嘅晚餐(臘腸雞飯)，飯氣攻心之下訓左4個鐘左右見口瓜瓜開咗支水嚟飲，發現好大陣燒燶咗嘅塑膠味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡單嚟講，屌你老母你舊嘢壞咗啊<br />\n我同個空姐講支水變咗，佢二話不說塞咗佢手頭上支水比我，聽都未聽哂我講嘢，唔通我同佢可以心靈感應。最搞笑嘅係，我話其實你吾信可以嗅下，屌那星佢索得唔夠0.5秒就話我地啲水一定唔會有事，你攞去。<br />\n我諗空姐一定覺得我同班蝗蟲一樣，落機前想攞返幾支水返香港留念<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW我唔係想屌鳩個空姐冇禮貌<br />\n我想講係我係一個幸運的人四百幾人得我一個中<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/154750_63b5de9aab92e05eb1de1369160f2056.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F154750_63b5de9aab92e05eb1de1369160f2056.png&h=39c751b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8afb3704d05967e75903fc325693c51f88dfb2fd","tid":744770,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"1fc451496096509c45d84e976b24b1344e441a2f","tid":744770,"uid":58071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0